This is where alignment tools will be wrapped.

To start reading usage:
<path-to-git-repository>/Alignment-Tools

To start an analysis with bwa aln:
<path-to-git-repository>/Alignment-Tools init bwa-aln <fastq-file> <relative-path-to-reference-genome.fasta> <options>
make

To get extra information about a command, use usage:
<path-to-git-repository>/Alignment-Tools init bwa-aln usage
